          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Moving Obstructed Trains In-between Openings Now (MOTION) Act</b></p> <p>Allows railroad employees to remain or go on duty for a period in excess of the limitations established under hours-of-service requirements to the extent necessary to clear a blockage of vehicular traffic at a grade crossing.</p>]]></text>
